headline: Oracle Stock Slides In Choppy Market For AI Stocks. What To Watch Next.
summary: Oracle stock tumbled Friday, joining a broad AI stocks pullback.  On the stock market today, Oracle stock is down more than 6% at 225.12 in afternoon trades.  While there is no clear catalyst for Oracle stock directly, stocks that have gotten a boost from optimism about generative AI were largely trading lower Friday.

headline: The AI Fears Dragging Markets Lower
summary: AI jitters are rattling through the stock market before traders jet for the Labor Day weekend.
